snippet.title: Mario + Rabbids Sparks of Hope - Rayman DLC Teaser Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The wacky Rabbids and Rayman reunite to embark on an exciting new adventure! Take on even more tactical fun when the Mario + Rabbids Sparks of Hope DLC arrives post-launch.

Mario + Rabbids Sparks of Hope releases for Nintendo Switch on October 20, 2022. Pre-orders available now: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/mario-plus-rabbids-sparks-of-hope-switch/
